um/sodium sulfates)." Braintree Laboratories, Braintree, MA.[2] "Product Information. Suclear (polyethylene glycol 3350 with electrolytes)." Braintree Laboratories, Braintree, MA.[3] "Product Information. Diovan (valsartan)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[4] "Product Information. Cozaar (losartan)." Merck & Co, Inc, West Point, PA.[5] "Product Information. Prepopik (citric acid/Mg oxide/Na picosulfate)." Ferring Pharmaceuticals Inc, Tarrytown, NY.[6] "Product Information. Golytely (polyethylene glycol electrolyte solution)." Braintree, Braintree, MA.', 1767369485);
