, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, More', NULL, 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/69978/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);
