e, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, Decitabine, More', 'Tetracycline, Rifamycin, Oxytetracycline, Famciclovir, Trifluridine, Cefuroxime, Benzylpenicillin, Ampicillin, Chlorhexidine, Povidone-iodine, Rifamycin, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/70058/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);
