d jaundice.', 'Synergism', 'Brivaracetam, Topiramate, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Lamotrigine, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Levetiracetam, Tiagabine, Oxcarbazepine, More', 'Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/70087/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);